      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TARA REBEL (4) held a forward position from the pinch but began to paddle on the bend and drifted out of the finish when 6th at this track in Grade 5 company. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Tough to beat if on-song. RHONDA FULL DAY (5) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished in the minors last time when third (17.66) at Taree Super Track making it back to back placings. Expecting another good run. GO FORWARD SKIP (1) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 4.5 lengths from the winner (23.80). Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Cannot be taken lightly. DON'T THINK SO (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
